                  </persName>
            . I was with Izard, and took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. That man would swear the ball of St. Paul's was only five yards round. I have no witnesses, I want none.</p>
